An example dataset consisting of pollock length, weight, and age data from Gulf of Alasks summer MACE surveys

pollock_length_weight_age_data.Rd

An example dataset consisting of pollock length, weight, and age data from Gulf of Alasks summer MACE surveys

Usage

pollock_length_weight_age_data

Format

A data frame with 19061 rows and 9 columns:

SURVEY

A unique identifier for each survey (numeric)

HAUL

An identifier for the trawl number that a specimen was captured in

SPECIES_CODE

An identifier for the species code for a given specimen

SUBCATEGORY

An identifier for the life history stage for a given specimen

FORK_LENGTH

pollock length (cm; numeric)

ORGANISM_WEIGHT

pollock weight (kg; numeric)

AGE

Pollock age (if available) (years; numeric)

REPORT_NUMBER

An identifier for the survey region in which a given specimen was captured (numeric)

region

An description of the survey region in which a given specimen was captured (character)

Source

Historic MACE reported values
